                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Respec<lb break="no" n="3"/>ti <expan><abbr>Sav</abbr><ex>aria</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Victo</abbr><ex cert="low">rinius</ex></expan> Mes<lb break="no" n="7"/>sor h<expan><ex>ere</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Westlich des Legionslagers in Wiederverwendung für ein spätantikes Grab gefunden. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Kranz, darüber ein Gorgoneion, Delphine, Pinienzapfen und Löwen; unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Reiter. Z. 6: statt Victo(rinius) auch Vict(orius) möglich.</p>
            </div>
